FilterDataOsMoSysIn
public class FilterDataOsMoSysIn.OmsResult
extends FilterDataOsMoSysIn.OmsTag

Class for results. It stores one or a table of values. In the former case, the value's key has the same name of the result tag. In the latter case, every value has its own key (defined in rsl file).
